variables.name: mIsEnabled
variables.comment: {@code true} to enable satellite and {@code false} to disable satellite

variables.name: mIsDemoMode
variables.comment:
* {@code true} to enable demo mode and {@code false} to disable. When disabling satellite,
     * {@code mIsDemoMode} is always considered as {@code false} by Telephony.

variables.name: mIsEmergencyMode
variables.comment:
* {@code true} means satellite is enabled for emergency mode, {@code false} otherwise. When
     * disabling satellite, {@code isEmergencyMode} is always considered as {@code false} by
     * Telephony.

methods.name: public boolean isEnabled()
methods.comment: * @return Whether satellite is to be enabled

methods.name: public boolean isDemoMode()
methods.comment: * @return Whether demo mode is to be enabled

methods.name: public boolean isEmergencyMode()
methods.comment: * @return Whether satellite is to be enabled for emergency mode
